MARC-File-MARCXML version 0.01
==================================

A subclass of MARC::File specific to the MARCXML format

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    MARC::Record
    XML::DOM
    XML::Writer

BUGS

    Any bugs should be reported to: https://github.com/NatLibFi/MARC-File-MARCXML

